    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/4d8c9acc79f16a5bb96e9d79b95e02dc.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个更加详细的描述，知道你想点什么——一顿破坏与混乱大餐。我们为您准备了一份简单的《 R.I.C.E》：充满戏剧性与辛辣而过于严肃的故事？完全错误。一大群抱怨个无止无休的角色？没有那些。街机游戏的简单快节奏战斗？这听上去不错。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Repetitive Indie Combat Experience》™是你在一天结束后所需要的一切。宝剑、腹肌、将行星变为星尘以及（最重要的）掠夺。没什么比得上犯下行星灭绝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/fcea9c206b2ed455551ff6dabdab42ec.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/884fde58eb085abb059695f367845e59.poster.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/884fde58eb085abb059695f367845e59.webm?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/884fde58eb085abb059695f367845e59.mp4?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，你没看错。你要杀光整个行星。在普通游戏中，你会先用棍子打老鼠、沿着食物链向上发展，在玩了两个小时后才被头目击败。在这儿正好相反。在每一场关中，你都可以杀戮整个生态系统，获得经验、多巴胺并升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，要是阵亡就没了。专家提示：死亡有害健康。不要死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/4b88c4954014aa04685c0901bca6b644.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/b5b583811e691299b9cfb9877589238a.poster.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/b5b583811e691299b9cfb9877589238a.webm?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/b5b583811e691299b9cfb9877589238a.mp4?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么要击杀行星呢？和你在其他游戏中杀戮的理由一样——为了获取战利品。最好的战利品来自一举摧毁整个文明以及他们居住的行星。快速消灭世界及其守护者，从而获得更新、更好的武器及其升级作为奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示二：有了更好的战利品便可更畅快淋漓地山路。不过，这点你早已知晓了吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/78200c663f73e92b2b1641dc2d64de2d.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/0f9a551f29a3b4b6965bde08d1c74c9f.poster.avif?t=1734718785\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/0f9a551f29a3b4b6965bde08d1c74c9f.webm?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2086140/extras/0f9a551f29a3b4b6965bde08d1c74c9f.mp4?t=1734718785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次不死并收集元货币™完成一关后，下一关便有更多的选择。每一张解锁的卡片都适用于任意武器及协同升级，以打造更强大的装备，比喻意义上的天空是你的极限（知道你将天空与其星球一起毁灭）。我们不做微小的平衡或改变单个数字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Repetitive Indie Combat Experience》将战斗提炼为最原始、最纯粹的形式，去除了一切阻碍——包括对你破坏能力的限制。你与你的《R.I.C.E.》之间毫无阻碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终提示：满足你原始的欲望——尽情杀戮并看着击杀数逐渐增长。</p>",
